Suzlon Energy to Buy Five Brazilian Wind Projects From Martifer

-- B y   S t e p h a n   N i e l s e n
-- 
2011-10-13T15:33:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/suzlon-energy-to-buy-five-brazilian-wind-projects-from-martifer.html
Suzlon Energy Ltd. (SUEL) ,  Asia ’s third-
biggest maker of  wind turbines , will purchase five wind farms in
 Brazil  from Martifer Renovaveis Geracao de Energia e
Participacoes SA.   Suzlon received permission to buy the wind farms from
electricity regulator Agencia Nacional de Energia Eletrica, the
Brasilia-based agency said in a statement Oct. 11. The purchase
amounts weren’t disclosed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephan Nielsen in Sao Paulo at 
 snielsen8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Wade at 
 wwade4@bloomberg.net  